Title: Do You Take Dexter Morgan?
Plot: It is the day before Dexter's wedding and Dexter must deal with two people targeting him, while preparing for his special occasion. Meanwhile, Angel tells Deb he's put her in for a promotion, but after he finds out some information her shield may be gone before she gets it.
GuestStars: Jason Manuel Olazabal, Christina Robinson, Preston Bailey, Tasia Sherel, Jeremy Overstreet, Jane McLean, Mary Alyce Kania, James Moses Black
